OL,5, John Bercow has appealed for his new   
OL,6, party's forgiveness as he addressed his
OL,7, "comrades" at Labour party conference. 
OL,9,FThe ex-Commons Speaker is attending the
OL,10,Fevent after joining the party in June. 
OL,12,FHe asked a crowd if he was permitted to
OL,13,Fcall them "comrades" - leading to      
OL,14,Fsurprised, but friendly, laughter over 
OL,15,Fhis use of the left wing term.         
OL,17,FAnd he asked the audience to forgive   
OL,18,Fhim for his Tory beginnings, hoping    
OL,19,Fthey believed in "the Rehabilitation of
OL,20,FOffenders Act".                        
